Package: dprint
Type: Package
Title: Print Tabular Data to Graphics Device
Version: 0.0.4
Date: 2017-11-15
Author: Carlin Brickner
Maintainer: Carlin Brickner <carlin.brickner.rpackage@gmail.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0)
Imports:
	grid, 
	stats,
	grDevices
Description: Provides a generalized method for printing tabular
    data within the R environment in order to make the process of presenting
    high quality tabular output seamless for the user. Utilizes a formula interface to
	specificy the attributes of a tables found in manuscripts or business reports.
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyLoad: yes
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: testthat
